ZH: 我们需要敦促政府采取更多措施来减少空气污染。
EN: We need to urge the government to take more measures to reduce air pollution.

ZH: 公司领导敦促员工提高工作效率。
EN: The company leaders urge the employees to improve work efficiency.

ZH: 我们应该敦促全社会共同关注儿童教育问题。
EN: We should urge the whole society to pay attention to children's education issues.

ZH: 学生会敦促校方增加校园安全措施。
EN: The student union urges the school to increase campus security measures.

ZH: 家长们敦促孩子们要好好学习，做个优秀的人。
EN: Parents urge their children to study hard and become outstanding individuals.

ZH: 我们应该敦促政府制定更加严格的环保法规。
EN: We should urge the government to enact stricter environmental protection laws.

ZH: 教师们敦促学生们积极参加课外活动。
EN: Teachers urge students to actively participate in extracurricular activities.

ZH: 运动员们互相敦促，鼓励对方取得更好的成绩。
EN: Athletes urge each other and encourage each other to achieve better results.

ZH: 领导们敦促员工积极参与社会公益活动。
EN: Leaders urge employees to actively participate in social welfare activities.

