EN: Supporters are urging the government to pay attention to public transportation construction.

ZH: 敦促他们早点行动，不要拖延时间。
EN: Urge them to act quickly and not procrastinate.

ZH: 他们敦促我尽快完成这个项目。
EN: They urged me to complete this project as soon as possible.

ZH: 她们敦促他们签署这份协议。
EN: They urged them to sign this agreement.

